ul.li: Signal Shield: Kernel ignores SIGKILL / SIGTERM from outside namespace unless explicitly handled.
Adoption: Any process whose parent dies is re-parented to this PID 1.
Namespace Death: When this process exits, the kernel immediately SIGKILLs all remaining processes in the namespace.
